{"tid":1448381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:31:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:40:15.000Z","uid":55628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5f4fdc8db48f89c585012de66eabab8f821c549c","tid":1448381,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:31:19.000Z","msg":"一人一 狂洗連登post [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvCIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=d64f3557\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvCIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=0d74d81a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"d83bda17c92477171ae61a3b58e3e0fd3e302a4d","tid":1448381,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:34:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"affcfdcec5f189e0354ffea35d4ba0aa16599ce5","tid":1448381,"uid":122676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:35:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c89b03dceaebda0a2dfc432262af671508de28e2","tid":1448381,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:35:14.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家"},{"pid":"1caba9a7e449ed8cad3f3033f3c55d2974c3c78a","tid":1448381,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:36:50.000Z","msg